---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact & Support"
  description="Get in touch with the developer or support VOID RTS development."
>
  <div class="container">

    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>Contact & Support</h1>
      <p>Solo dev project. Built from scratch. Every bit of feedback and support counts.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-page-grid">

      <section class="contact-section contact-section--msg">
        <div class="contact-section-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <g fill="#44aaff">
              <rect x="0" y="8" width="48" height="4"/>
              <rect x="0" y="12" width="4" height="24"/>
              <rect x="44" y="12" width="4" height="24"/>
              <rect x="0" y="36" width="48" height="4"/>
              <rect x="4" y="12" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="40" y="12" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="8" y="16" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="36" y="16" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="12" y="20" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="32" y="20" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="16" y="24" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="28" y="24" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="20" y="28" width="8" height="4"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>Got questions, feedback, bug reports, feature ideas, or just want to talk about the game? I read everything. Drop me an email and I'll get back to you.</p>
        <div class="contact-details">
          <span class="contact-name">Slawek</span>
          <a href="mailto:labienusX@gmail.com" class="contact-email">labienusX@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="contact-section contact-section--support">
        <div class="contact-section-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <g fill="#ff5544">
              <rect x="8" y="8" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="28" y="8" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="4" y="12" width="12" height="4"/>
              <rect x="24" y="12" width="12" height="4"/>
              <rect x="4" y="16" width="36" height="4"/>
              <rect x="4" y="20" width="36" height="4"/>
              <rect x="8" y="24" width="28" height="4"/>
              <rect x="12" y="28" width="20" height="4"/>
              <rect x="16" y="32" width="12" height="4"/>
              <rect x="20" y="36" width="4" height="4"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2>Support the Project</h2>
        <p>VOID RTS is a solo passion project built from scratch. If you like where this is heading and want to chip in, any support is genuinely appreciated. It helps cover tools, hosting, and keeps the momentum going.</p>
        <a href="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/AWYDN7ZAMM4JJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="paypal-btn paypal-btn--lg">
          Support via PayPal
        </a>
      </section>

    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
